95
00:03:32,790 --> 00:03:35,160
Marxism contains
three constitutive parts:

96
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:35,800
three.

97
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:38,620
philosophical one,
an economic one and a political one.

98
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:42,070
The philosophical part consists of
dialectical and historical materialism,

99
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:44,260
the economic part,
of the critique of political economy,

100
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:46,310
and the political part,
of scientific socialism.

101
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,040
These parts are
not isolated from each other, right?

102
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:51,420
They are not isolated.
They are intertwined

103
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:52,360
they interact.

104
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,460
In these three parts

105
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:56,750
reside the common bases
of any communist.

