very critical of monarchist politics.

117
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:20,990
Of Prussian monarchist politics.

118
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:24,600
In 1844,
he goes to France as an exile,

119
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:27,920
