138
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,450
They start to differ from
the Young Hegelians

139
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,750
and from Hegel himself.

140
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:15,110
This critique
that Marx and Engels do

141
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:17,030
