181
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:24,720
Are communists idealists?

182
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,300
Well,

183
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:28,670
little do people that never
got into contact with communism know

184
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:32,020
but communism appears
as a critique of utopianism

185
00:06:32,140 --> 00:06:33,720
and a critique of idealism.

186
00:06:33,770 --> 00:06:35,620
Marxism's philosophical pillar

187
00:06:35,660 --> 00:06:39,720
is constituted
as a critique of utopianisms and idealisms

188
00:06:39,770 --> 00:06:41,080
And that's what
