to present his party ideas,

1452
01:03:57,880 --> 01:04:00,580
that would become the Leninist Party
in Congress.

1453
01:04:00,580 --> 01:04:03,120
This book is a perfect example

1454
01:04:03,120 --> 01:04:07,060
