1466
01:04:30,780 --> 01:04:32,940
Here you can see
how he mastered the subject.

1467
01:04:33,020 --> 01:04:36,060
And finally, a part of Leninist theory
that I haven't mentioned

1468
01:04:36,110 --> 01:04:37,340
