just as important.

1469
01:04:37,390 --> 01:04:41,180
Lenin identifies
that capitalism has entered a new phase:

1470
01:04:41,200 --> 01:04:43,580
the imperialist phase.

1471
01:04:43,580 --> 01:04:47,600
Capitalism expands in such a way
that it becomes monopoly capitalism,

1472
01:04:47,630 --> 01:04:49,620
and the countries
at the center of capitalism

1473
01:04:49,640 --> 01:04:53,130
begin to dispute
the division of the territory of planet Earth

1474
01:04:53,290 --> 01:04:54,120
for resources.

1475
01:04:54,120 --> 01:04:57,440
Lenin theorizing
the new phase of capitalism

1476
01:04:57,550 --> 01:04:59,580
is what made
the Russian Revolution possible, folks.

1477
01:04:59,580 --> 01:05:02,940
So, this book here [Imperialism,
the Highest Stage of Capitalism] is essential,

1478
01:05:02,940 --> 01:05:06,000
because imperialism
is still our greatest enemy.

1479
01:05:06,000 --> 01:05:08,660
Understanding the role
of imperialism in global capitalism

1480
01:05:08,660 --> 01:05:11,580
is fundamental to
any revolutionary perspective, anyone.

